I swim twice a day and my goggles with -650 degrees correctional lens fare, wear and tear quickly and replacing them can be a challenge. I came to Megabox trying my luck on June 11, 2018 after work and was pleasantly surprised to find five pairs here. Noting the unexpected 20% discount, I bought four pairs and donated the receipt (with some residual value) to a charitable institution that loves animals!
Too many product for good.

A large department store in Kowloon Bay but quite far away from the residential area.  Better use the free shuttle service from the MTR station.  Many cashier inside the store so payment was fast.  Octopus card not accepted.  The price range was middle.
